high_descs: Move around from the bedroom and go to the sink.
Go near the sink and pick the pen.
Go back to the bedroom near the desklamp.
Switch on the desklamp with the needle.
anns.task_desc: Pick the pen from the sink to switch on the DeskLamp in the bed room

high_descs: Turn right and right again into the bathroom.
Pick up the pen from the sink.
Exit the bathroom and go to the desklamp on the right.
anns.task_desc: Hold a Pen under a lit DeskLamp.

high_descs: Turn right, move, turn right towards the sink in the toilet.
Turn around, move forward, turn right towards the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: To take the pen from sink, put the desk lamp on.
